### Problem13
##DFA2

Which of the following strings does this DFA accept?  

![image](/static/quiz/images/Users/carol/Desktop/CHAPTER05/../../../../5.1.6fig.jpg)  

**Choices:**

A. Bitstrings with at least one 1 

B. Bitstrings with equal number of occurrences of 01 and 10

C. Bitstrings with an equal number of occurrences of 0 and 1  

D. Bitstrings that end in 1   
### Quote
Coursera lecture slides <https://introcs.cs.princeton.edu/java/lectures/keynote/CS.14.IntroTheory.pdf>
choices: A. Bitstrings with at least one 1
B. Bitstrings with equal number of occurrences of 01 and 10
C. Bitstrings with an equal number of occurrences of 0 and 1
